        "description": "We need to separate the JNI elements from CMakeLists, with related modifications to the CI build scripts likely. Separating the JNI portion serves two related purposes:\r\n # Simplify building JNI code against precompiled lib arrow C++ code\r\n # Enable control of JNI build through Maven, rather than requiring Java devs to work with CMake directly\r\n\r\n[~dsusanibara]\r\n\r\n[~kou]\u00a0",
